title: CND: Treatments/Prep Stickey Base Coat, 2.3 oz
description: A soft, "sticky" base coat designed to anchor nail enamel to the nail. Acts as a gripping agent to prevent peeling and chipping. Ideal for both natural nails and enhancements.

title: DL Professional Dotting Tool with Nail Art Brush
description: Debra lynn professional dotting tool with nail art brush which can be used to create flowers and marble designs. 2 sided nail art tool, one side is a dotting tool and the other is a nail art brush. Great FPR making smooth curves.

title: MASH Nail Art Brush Cleaner Cup
description: The Brush Cleaner jar can hold brushes of various sizes and can be used with all brands of brush cleaning solution. Comes with a screw on lid to prevent evaporation of brush cleaning solution when not in use.MASH-Keeping it Fresh
